{"words":[{"word":"ain't","count":3},{"word":"dark","count":3},{"word":"heard","count":2},{"word":"i've","count":2},{"word":"bad","count":2},{"word":"thinking","count":2},{"word":"maybe","count":2},{"word":"dissociation","count":2},{"word":"worse","count":2},{"word":"start","count":2},{"word":"sovereign","count":2},{"word":"tide","count":2},{"word":"feeling","count":2},{"word":"said","count":1},{"word":"priestess","count":1},{"word":"playername","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"stationed","count":1},{"word":"camp","count":1},{"word":"longer","count":1},{"word":"memory","count":1},{"word":"either","count":1},{"word":"tide's","count":1},{"word":"crawled","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"head","count":1},{"word":"suffering","count":1},{"word":"side","count":1},{"word":"effect","count":1},{"word":"exposure","count":1},{"word":"word","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"close","count":1},{"word":"end","count":1},{"word":"seeing","count":1},{"word":"things","count":1},{"word":"hallucinations","count":1},{"word":"delusions","count":1},{"word":"works","count":1},{"word":"'em","count":1},{"word":"far","count":1},{"word":"dead","count":1},{"word":"calling","count":1},{"word":"tacet","count":1},{"word":"discords","count":1},{"word":"built","count":1},{"word":"knows","count":1},{"word":"swallowed","count":1},{"word":"came","count":1},{"word":"used","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"grip","count":1},{"word":"ah","count":1},{"word":"worked","count":1},{"word":"yet","count":1},{"word":"anyway","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"solid","count":1},{"word":"name","count":1},{"word":"happens","count":1},{"word":"kinds","count":1},{"word":"ways","count":1},{"word":"different","count":1},{"word":"person","count":1},{"word":"any","count":1},{"word":"rate","count":1},{"word":"problem","count":1},{"word":"perception","count":1},{"word":"folks","count":1},{"word":"eat","count":1},{"word":"life","count":1},{"word":"others","count":1},{"word":"real","count":1},{"word":"keep","count":1},{"word":"away","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"alright","count":1},{"word":"rest","count":1},{"word":"bit","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"looks","count":1},{"word":"augusta's","count":1},{"word":"finally","count":1},{"word":"faced","count":1},{"word":"doubting","count":1},{"word":"talk","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"I heard what you said to the Priestess, {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"No... I've never even heard of her.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"You should know, I've been stationed in this camp longer than most. Memory ain't bad, either.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Been thinking... Maybe the Dark Tide's crawled into your head. Could be you're suffering from dissociation, a side effect of all that exposure.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Word is, people who get too close end up seeing things. Hallucinations, delusions, the works.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Some of 'em go as far as thinking they see the dead. Or worse, some start calling themselves Tacet Discords.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"The Sovereign was built from the Dark Tide itself. Who knows what it swallowed before it came for us? Could be worse than what you're used to. You must be in its grip.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Ah, don't get too worked up. It ain't that bad, not yet anyway.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"See, the thing is, it's not like there's one solid name for it. Happens in all kinds of ways, different for each person. And…","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"At any rate, dissociation is just a problem in perception.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"Some folks let it eat at them for life. Others know what's real and what ain't. They keep away from the Dark Tide, and before long they start feeling alright.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"How are you feeling? You need to rest up a bit? ...Oh, looks like Augusta's finally here.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001},{"text":"She's been through it too, faced the Sovereign just like you. If you're still doubting, maybe talk to her. Could help.","quest_name":"By Moon's Fated Light","quest_id":886000001}]}